                            <comment id="15244512" author="thiru_mg" created="Sun, 17 Apr 2016 02:59:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is the patch, which a variation of the one submitted by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=zolyfarkas&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;zolyfarkas&quot;&gt;Zoltan Farkas&lt;/a&gt;, which instead of backtracking at the end, advances the position only when needed.&lt;/p&gt;

